description: Erection of new buildings to provide: i) new sixth form centre comprising a 2/4 storey building with central atrium to provide performing arts, catering, sport, media, music and ICT facilities with 98 car park spaces, new access and 2.4m high perimeter fencing (full); ii) new 3 /4 storey residential buildings to provide 48 x 1 bed, 61 x 2 bed, 13 x 3 bed and 1 x 4 bed units (all affordable) with 68 car parking spaces and new access (full); and  iii) new 70 bed care home for the elderly with associated parking and access from College Road (outline)
